---
// Popup: We do not use cookies on this website. We respect your privacy.
---

<div
    class="fixed bottom-4 max-w-xs left-4 py-2.5 px-4 z-50 rounded-lg bg-background border border-border/20"
>
    <div>
        We doesn't use third party cookies - only a single in-house cookie. No
        data is sent to a third party.
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-2">
        <button class="border border-border/20 rounded-md px-2 py-1">
            Accept
        </button>
        <button class="border border-border/20 rounded-md px-2 py-1">
            Decline
        </button>
    </div>
</div>
